channel.title: End of Saturday BM tf2 night
channel.description:
The (unofficial) [url=https://forums.blackmesasource.com/showthread.php?t=2446]BM tf2 night[/url] started about 2.5 hours ago and effectively ended about some minutes ago.
I hope everyone who was there had a great time! And I'm sorry for those that couldn't come...
Anyway, this thread is for discussing what you thought of the event and thoughts or suggestions for the next event(including which game or mod we'll play then!)
Edit: DAMN TYPO
